{"tid":1900707,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「幫港出聲」周融現於翠雅山房接受隔離","createTime":"2020-02-27T11:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T14:28:11.000Z","uid":7692,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d32b82f937a8752c23fcc7bde50ae99e5c9cc7f3","tid":1900707,"uid":7692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:22:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%B9%AB%E6%B8%AF%E5%87%BA%E8%81%B2-%E5%91%A8%E8%9E%8D-%E6%9B%BE%E8%88%87%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%BB%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%A9%9A%E5%AE%B4-%E7%8F%BE%E6%96%BC%E7%BF%A0%E9%9B%85%E5%B1%B1%E6%88%BF%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%2581%25B2-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E8%259E%258D-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A9%259A%25E5%25AE%25B4-%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%2596%25BC%25E7%25BF%25A0%25E9%259B%2585%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%2F&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgfdnC8dk%2FAL47v0imjzWEG4%3D&h=5df8f7ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%2581%25B2-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E8%259E%258D-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A9%259A%25E5%25AE%25B4-%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%2596%25BC%25E7%25BF%25A0%25E9%259B%2585%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%2F&h=cf4d6727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%B9%AB%E6%B8%AF%E5%87%BA%E8%81%B2-%E5%91%A8%E8%9E%8D-%E6%9B%BE%E8%88%87%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E9%A6%AC%E4%B8%BB%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%A9%9A%E5%AE%B4-%E7%8F%BE%E6%96%BC%E7%BF%A0%E9%9B%85%E5%B1%B1%E6%88%BF%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2/</a><br />\n<br />\n居於大坑瑞士花園的商人兼馬主周巧兒，前日（25日）確診武漢肺炎。周巧兒於確診前 3 日（22日)，曾於金鐘萬豪酒店出席一場婚禮飯宴，「幫港出聲」召集人周融承認當日亦有出席，現於翠雅山房接受隔離。<br />\n<br />\n周融今日（27日）接受《立場新聞》電話查詢時承認，曾於本月 22 日到金鐘萬豪酒店，出席與確診者周巧兒同場的婚禮飯宴，昨日開始於翠雅山房檢疫中心接受隔離，現時未有出現任何病徵。<br />\n<br />\n對於會否擔心感染，周融表示：「唔擔心，擔心咩姐，我又冇嘢<br />\n<br />\n他指當天婚宴共有兩圍食飯，約 20 多人出席，均被視作確診者的密切接觸者，已接受隔離，全部人沒有任何病徵。他又說「最緊要係自己處之泰然，不要太緊張，靜十多日喺呢到睇吓書。」<br />\n<br />\n確診的周巧兒是周融的侄女，他當日是出席其侄孫女的一場婚禮。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君今日於記者會指，周巧兒於本月 22 日出席一個結婚儀式。張竹君說，她早上到位於大坑的竹麗苑參與一對新人的斟荼儀式，然後到北角柏尉山一座參與簽紙儀式，再於金鐘萬豪酒店包廳兩檯食飯。"},{"pid":"a13c6d6462ca501a055cce54feabf53c669d1ef6","tid":1900707,"uid":85659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />武漢肺炎加油!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1c4477d39c814428f8fb715c5231eb7f9b3517","tid":1900707,"uid":7692,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"呢個病真係好針對性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048e62f12d882e7a5affbb29c1e87a6714c1390d","tid":1900707,"uid":3241,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:24:12.000Z","msg":"點解永遠賤人閪人都有得住酒店級<br />\n一般市民就住垃圾康樂營"},{"pid":"7e5763ed7ee7bf91f8825ff1059601a65e2dac99","tid":1900707,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f1c4477d39c814428f8fb715c5231eb7f9b3517","tid":1900707,"uid":7692,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"呢個病真係好針對性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T11:24:26.000Z","msg":"只有奶共先會重去支那<br />\n去得支那咪奶囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" cla